last_episode_to_air.name: Financial Freedom in Fort Worth
last_episode_to_air.overview: A woman gets to live her dream of being a stay-at-home mom when her husband lands a new job in Fort Worth, TX. However, he must start his new position immediately and they are in a rush to find their forever home.

name: House In A Hurry
overview: Finding the right house to buy is stressful and, for some, can take months or even years. However, unexpected relocations and compelling situations force these homebuyers to find the perfect property in an unfamiliar city in just one weekend.
